entries.femaleVariant: So how you all been? Hangin' in?
Yeah, same ol', same ol'. Pad's rustin' up, gonna have to grab some more sheet iron.
Man, how's it we live in a hood with some fucking preem hotel, and we're wasting away in these tin cans?
Voodoo Boys should do something. Y'know, for the people.
Hey, leave 'em. I'm just happy I don't have to worry about no city gangs comin' out here.
Yeah, 'stead you gotta worry about acid rain and where you're getting your next can of scop.
Can't have everything. Just gotta keep on keepin' on.
